      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC81b732a825a3100582b5b7cf0bc2f3d2"></a>Removal of the timing gears
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16601"> </a>Remove the oil sump guard (<a href="78006.html#DUCdebde6802aa910058bbaf20939ae18d2">Removing the oil sump guard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16606"> </a>Drain the engine oil (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16611"> </a>Remove the sprocket cover (<a href="79974.html#DUC678e5bc82b2410058de4ee3905e05ec4">Removing the front sprocket</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16616"> </a>Remove the clutch slave cylinder (<a href="78738.html#DUC1e4714c82b2410058cedd30e2bfae6c4">Removing the clutch slave cylinder</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16621"> </a>Drain the cooling system (<a href="77257.html#DUCf34a5aa829f91005800d816ce97b3fd2">Changing the coolant</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16626"> </a>Remove the pump-cylinder hoses (<a href="45114.html#DUCad1f8410256a10058d3dd14d9928c7d2">Removing the cylinder/piston assembly</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16631"> </a>Remove the water pump/radiator pipes (<a href="44924.html#DUCc06658c8250110058a838a10427928d2">Removing cooling system pipes and unions</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16636"> </a>Remove the generator cover and the flywheel/generator unit (<a href="45174.html#DUCf616ff28259110058912eb60359b4bd2">Removing the generator cover</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16642"> </a>Slide out driving gear (A) of timing gear pair (1), spacer (7) and remove key (2).
         </div>
      </div>
