      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16651"> </a>Straighten out the lockwasher (3) of nut (4).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16653"> </a>Restrain the driven timing gear by inserting a pin in one of the holes, and unscrew the nut (4).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16655"> </a>Remove nut (4), washer (3), driven timing gear (B) and key (5) from the timing layshaft.
         </div>
      </div>
